Target: OntoSchool is an ontology to represent schools and their information such as (contact information, address, CCAs etc).

Comment: An educational institution designed to provide learning spaces and learning environments for the teaching of students under the direction of teachers.
Label: School

Comment: Educational institutions funded and managed by the government.
Label: Government school

Comment: Educational institutions that receive partial funding from the government but are managed independently.
Label: Government aided school

Comment: Educational institutions that are not administered by the government.
Label: Independent school

Comment: Educational institutions that focus on a specific area of study or cater to students with particular needs or interests.
Label: Specialised school

Comment: Educational institutions that are not administered by the government and focuses on a specific area of study or cater to students with particular needs or interests.
Label: Specialised independent school

Comment: Groups for different types of CCAs (Co-Curricular Activities).
Label: CCA groups

Comment: Physical sports CCAs involve activities focused on physical fitness, teamwork, and competitive sportsmanship.
Label: Physical sports

Comment: Visual and performing arts CCAs encompass a wide range of creative activities including drawing, painting, sculpture, photography, dance, drama, music, and choir.
Label: Visual and performing arts

Comment: Clubs and societies CCAs cover a diverse array of interests and hobbies beyond sports and arts.
Label: Clubs and societies

Comment: Uniformed groups CCAs involve organizations that promote leadership, discipline, and community service through structured programs and activities.
Label: Uniformed groups

Comment: Student leadership CCAs focus on developing leadership skills, responsibility, and initiative among students.
Label: Student leadership

Comment: An activity or program that complements the academic curriculum in educational institutions.
Label: CCA

Comment: A stage or phase of formal education that an individual has completed or is currently pursuing.
Label: Education level

Comment: This level focuses on fundamental skills such as literacy, numeracy, and basic knowledge in subjects like science, social studies, and language arts.
Label: Primary education

Comment: This level builds upon the foundational knowledge acquired in primary school and offers more specialized subjects and opportunities for academic exploration.
Label: Secondary education

Comment: This level offers advanced coursework, preparation for college or university admissions, and opportunities for students to pursue specialized subjects or interests in preparation for further academic study.
Label: Junior college

Comment: This level provides specialized knowledge and skills in various academic disciplines or professional fields and prepares individuals for careers or advanced study.
Label: Tertiary education

Comment: This level integrate multiple education levels or age groups to provide a more flexible and inclusive learning environment.
Label: Mixed levels

Comment: The distribution of students based on their gender or sex.
Label: Gender composition

Comment: An educational setting or institution where students of only one gender are enrolled.
Label: Monogender

Comment: An educational setting or institution where only male students are enrolled.
Label: All boys

Comment: An educational setting or institution where only female students are enrolled.
Label: All girls

Comment: An educational setting or institution where students of both genders—males and females—are enrolled together.
Label: Coeducational

Comment: A relationship which decribes the CCA groups in a school.
Label: has CCA groups

Comment: A relationship which decribes the different activities or programmes under each CCA group.
Label: has CCA

Comment: A relationship which describes the contact number of a school.
Label: has contact number

Comment: A relationship which describes the education level that a school provides.
Label: has education level

Comment: A relationship which describes the gender composition of a school (Boys only, girls only, mixed).
Label: has gender composition

Comment: A relationship that relates a school to its built structures.
Label: has property

Comment: A relationship that describes a school's address.
Label: has address

Comment: Programmes offered by the school.
Label: offers programme

Comment: Website of the school.
Label: hasWeb Site

Comment: Email address of a school.
Label: has email
